   626	| ----------------- | ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
   627	| Root              | `<div>`    | `data-ars-scope="range-slider"`, `data-ars-orientation` |
   628	| Label             | `<label>`  | Group label                                             |
   629	| Track             | `<div>`    | Pointer interaction target                              |
   630	| Range             | `<div>`    | Filled region between thumbs                            |
